summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 2.5°C) and outside temperature (up 2.4°C) and drier conditions in rainfall (down 0.2 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in light levels (up 3292 lux), cloud levels (down 138 m), and pressure (up 5 mbar).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 5178 lux), cloud levels (up 156 m), and feels like temperature (up 1.7°C) when compared to today.
